Mercenary
A professional soldier for hire with solid combat and survival training,
adaptable and loyal to whoever is paying. Mercenary is an alias for the
merc soldier OCC.

Skill categories: Military, Physical, Espionage, Pilot, Technical, W.P.
Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
Starting equipment: Body armor, two ranged weapons, combat knife, radio,
and mercenary contracts or unit affiliation.
